The MAC VM does not display at full screen 
 
1. Input following at the start of the VMX file 
bosi.forceSetupOnce="TRUE" 
2. Enter Setup -> Boot from a file -> Recovery HD -> com.apply.recovery.boot -> boot.efi 
3. Select a language 
4. Input the following command in Terminal 
csrutil disable 
5. reboot, then reinstall the tools 
-------------------------------------------------- 

